                            </msItem>
                            
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.7">
                                <locus from="53v" to="65r"/>
                                <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5354Mashaf#PartSix">Maṣḥafa ʾahagʷǝlota ḥasat, Part 6</title>
                            </msItem>
                            
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.8">
                                <locus target="#65r"/>
                                <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5354Mashaf#Colophon">Maṣḥafa ʾahagʷǝlota ḥasat, Colophon</title>
                                <note>The following is the complete text of the embedded colophon.
                                It states that the work was composed in 1875, and that <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3451DeJacob">Giustino De Jacobis</persName>, called here ‘apostle of Ethiopia’ was sent there by
                                    pope <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS4820Gregory">Gregory XVI (1831–1846)</persName> in the
                                    year <date when="1839" calendar="ethiopian" when-custom="1831">1831 A.M. (1839)</date>.
                                </note>
                                <incipit xml:lang="am">አነ፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS12520TaklaH">ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡</persName> ወልዱ፡ ለካህን፡
                                    <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS12521TaklaE">ተክለ፡ እግዚእ፡</persName>
                                    ዘማርያም፡ ሰዊቶ፡ እንተ፡ ሀገረ፡ <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC7186Memsah">መምሳሕ፡</placeName> ጸሐፍኩ፡ ዛተ፡ ንስቲተ፡ 
                                    መጽሐፈ፡ <date when="1875">በ፲፰፸፭፡ ዓመተ፡ ሥጋዌ፡</date> ለአሕጕሎተ፡ ሐሰት፡ ዘተነግረት፡ በላዕለ፡ ጻድቅ፡ 
                                    አቡነ፡ ህየንተ፡ ሐዋርያ፡ ዘኢትዮጵያ፡ 
                                    ዘፈነዎ፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS4820Gregory">ጎርጎርዮስ፡</persName> በስም፡ ፲፮፡ ርእሰ፡ ሊቃነ፡ ጳጳሳት፡ ዘሮም፡ ለሰቢከ፡ ወንጌለ፡ እግዚእነ፡ <sic>የሱስ፡</sic>
                                    ክርስቶስ፡ <date when="1839" calendar="ethiopian" when-custom="1831">፲፰፴፩፡ ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት።</date>
                                </incipit>
                            </msItem>
                        </msItem>
                        
                    
